{"tid":1644597,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"NBA tweet 其實唔覺意掀起咗另一場美國嘅本土戰...","createTime":"2019-10-10T15:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T17:11:39.000Z","uid":271601,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2edffa2786f5098d5f63fadf9761fb1fe2d46b94","tid":1644597,"uid":271601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:17:21.000Z","msg":"就係 Trump 陣營嘅反攻：<br />\n<img src=\"https://twt-thumbs.washtimes.com/media/image/2019/09/30/Warriors_Media_Day_Basketball_18882.jpg-9f765_c0-126-2051-1321_s885x516.jpg?fca04d7ec022e90f82df806e38397c5465d1d084\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwt-thumbs.washtimes.com%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2019%2F09%2F30%2FWarriors_Media_Day_Basketball_18882.jpg-9f765_c0-126-2051-1321_s885x516.jpg%3Ffca04d7ec022e90f82df806e38397c5465d1d084&h=f73c1d12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>Outspoken anti-Trump NBA coach goes mum on league's China politics: 'No comment'<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2019/oct/8/steve-kerr-nbas-outspoken-trump-critic-goes-mum-on\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtontimes.com%2Fnews%2F2019%2Foct%2F8%2Fsteve-kerr-nbas-outspoken-trump-critic-goes-mum-on&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5adOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=3ce12d4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2019/oct/8/steve-kerr-nbas-outspoken-trump-critic-goes-mum-on</a></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美國嘅體育界，不嬲對政治都好 outspoken，佢哋一場跪國歌事件搞到滿城風雨，對國內嘅平權問題亦非常踴躍發言，不過一講到中国呢，即刻變咗羔羊...<br />\n<blockquote>U.S. national anthem protests<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Since August 2016, some American athletes have protested against police brutality and racism by kneeling during the U.S. national anthem. Since 2017, many players also began protesting against President Donald Trump's criticisms of those involved in the protest as well as against Trump's policies since taking office.</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/gvTCRk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FgvTCRk&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5adOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=8c776a04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/gvTCRk</a></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n荷里活都一模一樣，一眾藝人平時對政治表態毫不留情，但對中国呢，就算係美國隊長嘅所謂發聲，講真，小弟唔肯定佢係咪真係講香港，佢轉頭話係支持彈劾 Trump 都得嘅：<br />\n<blockquote>I think everyone who chooses to stay out of politics(which is your right) should make a mental note of where they would draw the line and feel it necessary to get involved. Then ask yourself, is it possible that point already happened, but it happened too slowly to notice.<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/ChrisEvans/status/1181265470260994049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChrisEvans%2Fstatus%2F1181265470260994049&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5adOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=c819bcb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChrisEvans%2Fstatus%2F1181265470260994049&h=84da05eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ChrisEvans/status/1181265470260994049</a></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢種落差，Trump 陣營一向詬病，就算係激進環保團體如 Green Peace，你有冇見過佢哋挑機中石油／中海油？<br />\n<br />\n中国話題之前一直難以成為美國本土焦點，因為太過抽離。譬如新疆集中營，美國平民真係唔理得咁多，佢哋自己本土大把問題。或者活摘器官，疑幻疑真，除咗大紀元，有聲譽嘅報社甚少著墨，一般平民只會當係小道消息消化，唔會當真，難以激起民憤。<br />\n<br />\n但今次嘅 NBA 事件就好唔同，香港受關注嘅程度已經係國家級，一般平民都會有判斷，而美國本土發言俾美國人睇，亦覺得貼身，但原來距離中国萬里之外，講句差不多全美媒體有共識嘅說話都要問准中国㗎！<br />\n<br />\n面對呢個良機，pro-Trump 媒體仲唔乘機報仇咩。不過撇開陣營之間嘅恩怨，或者真正值得關注嘅係，會唔會令美國民間產生一種新共識？就係 Trump 唔係真係咁大問題，大家唔好再講佢喇，因為真正嘅美國國家危機係中国崛起！原來中国已經入侵國土，可以直接控制美國人點講嘢，縱使什麼「傷害14億人民感情」嘅理由係廢話，因為嗰1 4億，大部份根本用唔到 twitter 睇 #StandWithHK 嘅 tweet...<br />\n<br />\n美國嘅兩極化，唔係始於今日，我最鍾意講嘅歷史，就係1941年嘅美國，當時國內有參戰嘅聲音，但亦有 Why Not Peace With Hitler 嘅大遊行。結果呢，就係偷襲珍珠港解困，冇人再可以反戰，美國人終於有共識。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C4GRFbfWYAAyXxr?format=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC4GRFbfWYAAyXxr%3Fformat%3Djpg&h=73535991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>&quot;Why Not Peace with Hitler?&quot; Anti-War Protest in NYC, July 7, 1941<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/choplogik/status/829103483219492868\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchoplogik%2Fstatus%2F829103483219492868&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5adOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=402a1b0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchoplogik%2Fstatus%2F829103483219492868&h=867d50cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/choplogik/status/829103483219492868</a></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今日 NBA 嘅衝擊未及珍珠港嘅力度，但亦唔排除已經足夠推動範式轉移，因為民意已經醞釀咗一年：<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pewresearch.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/FT_19.09.30_China_Negative-views-China-up-sharply-Canada-US.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2FFT_19.09.30_China_Negative-views-China-up-sharply-Canada-US.png&h=797f9a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>People around the globe are divided in their opinions of China<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://www.pewresearch.org/fact-tank/2019/09/30/people-around-the-globe-are-divided-in-their-opinions-of-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Ffact-tank%2F2019%2F09%2F30%2Fpeople-around-the-globe-are-divided-in-their-opinions-of-china&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5adOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=79c2d7c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pewresearch.org/fact-tank/2019/09/30/people-around-the-globe-are-divided-in-their-opinions-of-china</a></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今次香港發出嘅政治能量驚人，唔係講笑，我哋唔止團結咗自己，甚至團結埋美國。團結美國係非常重要嘅一環，因為美國政治往往呈現兩極化現象，國內力量互相抵銷之下貌似弱國，但有事件觸發團結嘅話，超人 mode 就會突然出現。二戰，美國遲遲唔肯參戰，就係覺得自己力量不足，無謂陪葬，但珍珠港令團結狀態出現，美國方知自己原來咁勁...<br />\n<br />\n當然，美國嘅團結唔係咁易俾你睇到，媒體會照樣互相批評，說話難聽，但核心行動無障礙，呢個已經夠嚇死人。"},{"pid":"ffacd3019a3176c19862c1fe1de6ea5077057db1","tid":1644597,"uid":332797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"突發！美國人要大家教佢點抵制暴雪！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644598</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7c94426e3bb92df5552357797c5797af4bb6ba06","tid":1644597,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:39:36.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa9545b71d5a4a1151526628bddaeb4642b662fa","tid":1644597,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T08:59:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf2a9ae8a32a4af000d541fe4e60f2769550fb3","tid":1644597,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:00:17.000Z","msg":"香港幫美國ko咗內亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8125134f04abb8798cfea9081bd8f804537dd192","tid":1644597,"uid":27319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:02:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5571ebe5c1740fa869537943d9359269a9548764","tid":1644597,"uid":218313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:06:18.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔好睇小自己<br />\n我地改變緊世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4becc8a8c730ffe0c756f24e077d90ca5df272b2","tid":1644597,"uid":286792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-